Utiliser les technologies du Web :

Throughout this documentation, youll see references to the standard Web APIs that SvelteKit builds on top of. Rather than reinventing the wheel, we use the platform, which means your existing web development skills are applicable to SvelteKit. Conversely, time spent learning SvelteKit will help you be a better web developer elsewhere.
